<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>

<p>Two <rs type="material" key="marmor">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">architrave</rs> blocks, incorporating architrave and <rs type="decoration">frieze</rs>: a. complete (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">2.80</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.67</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.67</measure>); b. broken at left, damaged below, and a fragment added at the right end in 1982 (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">1.63</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.69</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.55</measure>). Above, a decoration of <rs type="decoration">heads</rs> and <rs type="decoration">masks</rs> in relief; below, a simple moulding, and below that two fasciae.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text"><head>Description of Text</head><p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on both fasciae.</p>
</div><div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>l.1, <measure dim="none">0.07</measure>; l.2, <measure dim="none">0.065</measure></p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date notBefore="0001" notAfter="0100" exact="none">First century  A.D.</date> (<rs type="criteria">...</rs>)</p>
</div>
